statements.sql: select `t_booking`.`booking_id`, `t_booking`.`patient_id`, `t_booking`.`booking_date`, `t_booking`.`booking_start_time`, `t_booking`.`booking_total_time`, `t_booking`.`facility_id`, `t_booking`.`facility_id`, `t_booking`.`service_1`, `t_booking`.`service_1_kind`, `t_booking`.`service_2`, `t_booking`.`service_2_kind`, `t_booking`.`doctor_id`, `t_booking`.`hygienist_id`, `tf1`.`facility_id`, `tf1`.`facility_name`, `t_booking`.`clinic_id`, `t_booking`.`booking_group_id` from `t_booking` left join `t_facility` as `tf1` on `t_booking`.`facility_id` = `tf1`.`facility_id` where `t_booking`.`patient_id` is null and `t_booking`.`last_kind` <> '9' and `t_booking`.`clinic_id` = '13' and date(`booking_date`) >= '2016-08-08' group by `booking_group_id` order by `t_booking`.`booking_id` asc limit 21 offset 0
select `facility_name`, `facility_id` from `t_facility` where `last_kind` <> '9' order by `facility_id` asc
select `treatment_name`, `treatment_id` from `m_treatment` where `last_kind` <> '9' order by `treatment_id` asc
select `service_name`, `service_id` from `m_service` where `last_kind` <> '9' order by `service_sort_no` asc
